; perception-pipeline.form — the whole toolkit, composed: raw signal in, believed recognition out.
;
; THE CAPSTONE. The six toolkit bricks (feature-vector, nearest-shape, sequence-predictor,
; classifier-eval, novelty, temporal-smoothing) are each proven alone. This wires the recognition
; path into ONE end-to-end flow and proves the COMPOSITION runs, three-way (Go=Rust=TS). It is the
; showable shape of everything tonight: the body sensing for itself, no foreign model in the loop.
;
; THE FLOW  (runnable: form-stdlib/perception-pipeline.fk · proven: tests/perception-pipeline-band.fk -> 127)
;
;   raw signal window (a list of numbers a carrier hands in)
;     -> fv-histogram        bin the window into a fixed-width feature vector
;     -> ns-label/ns-strength route the feature to the interned prototype it agrees with most
;     -> nv-recognized?      gate: the recognized label, or "novel" when below the recognition floor
;     -> ts-stable           believe a label only when it persists across the last k frames, else silence
;
;   pp-read   (signal thresholds nbins prototypes floor)        — one frame: a recognized label or "novel"
;   pp-stable (signals thresholds nbins prototypes floor k)     — the believed recognition over a window,
;                                                                 or "" when the field is novel or unsettled
;
; WHAT THE PROOF SHOWS (band, verdict 127): a dog-shaped signal window classifies to "dog" with its
; exact strength surviving the whole composition; a different window reads "cat"; a window matching no
; prototype is gated to "novel" instead of forced into a wrong label; three steady frames are believed
; as "dog"; and a single noise frame at the front breaks belief into honest silence until it ages out.
; Every bit walks the FULL pipeline, not a stage in isolation.
;
; WHY IT MATTERS: this is the body's own perception, end to end, with no third party in the loop —
; its own feature, its own classifier (content-addressed: a prototype is a substrate cell, the same
; on every device by NodeID), its own sense of the new, its own patience. A carrier (mic, camera, a
; phone sensor, a declared now-playing) only has to hand the pipeline a window of numbers; the seeing
; is Form, proven identical across three kernels, shareable across bodies. The self-grounding loop
; then grades this pipeline against the routes we already trust, and promotes it to "self" where it
; earns the right — so the pipeline that is cheap today becomes trusted tomorrow.
;
; KIN: feature-vector.form · nearest-shape.form · novelty.form · temporal-smoothing.form (the stages) ·
;   recognition-router.form (fuse several such pipelines / models) · self-grounding-perception.form
;   (grade and promote it) · declared-source.form (skip it when a source already declared the truth) ·
;   shared-sensing.form (run it on many bodies, one field) · lc-honest-lane (silence over a forced label).
;
; LINEAGE: the satsang / presence listener wanted a body that senses for itself; tonight's toolkit
;   built the organs; this is them breathing together — one recipe, raw field in, honest recognition out.
